-MerchantsofQeynos <br>
-AntoniusBayle <br>
-CoalitionofTradefolk <br>
-GuardsofQeynos <br>
+CircleOfUnseenHands <br>
<br>
Anyone know if this is true? From what the faction hits says it doesnt seem to do anything to our epic faction. Thx <p>Feynan Escafon'ea<br>
Level 52 Channeler<br>
"Those who cannot, don't. Those who can, keep casting."
