<br>
It doesn't affect your faction for completing the epic... but it does make visiting Dargon in Halas a lot more exciting.  Of course, the first wizard to complete the epic was a dark elf, so I certainly wouldn't worry about it too much.<br>
<br>
I completed the Band of Rodcet Nife quest a long time ago, and that made me KoS to barbarians because of that damn dog in West Karana...<br>
